'Or whether the name comes from your trade . 
But the stony one is a gruff one likewise , and that hazy state of his is always an uncertain state , highly conscious of its dignity , and prone to take offence . 
Sometimes the stones hit him , and sometimes they miss him , but Durdles seems indifferent to either fortune . 
'What are you doing to the man ? demands Jasper , stepping out into the moonlight from the shade . 
'Making a cock shy of him , replies the hideous small boy . 
'Give me those stones in your hand . 
