I am a particularly Angular man , proceeded Mr. Grewgious , as if it suddenly occurred to him to mention it , 'and I am not used to give anything away . 
If , for these two reasons , some competent Proxy would give YOU away , I should take it very kindly . 
Rosa intimated , with her eyes on the ground , that she thought a substitute might be found , if required . 
