As you say , Mr. Crisparkle , interposed the Dean , nodding his head smoothly , 'there is nothing else to be done . 
No doubt , no doubt . 
There is no alternative , as your good sense has discovered . 
'I am entirely satisfied of his perfect innocence , sir , nevertheless . 
'We e ell ! said the Dean , in a more confidential tone , and slightly glancing around him , 'I would not say so , generally . 
