'So I believe , and I hope I may live to know it . 
Such a good friend and helper ! He took the fortifying hand from his shoulder , and kissed it . 
Mr. Crisparkle beamed at the books , but not so brightly as when he had entered . 
The Minor Canon's Cathedral duties made these visits of his difficult to accomplish , and only to be compassed at intervals of many weeks . 
But they were as serviceable as they were precious to Neville Landless . 
When they had got through such studies as they had in hand , they stood leaning on the window sill , and looking down upon the patch of garden . 
